data.description: This captivating residence, nestled in a serene community, graces a lush one-acre parcel. The moment you step inside, the inviting embrace of natural hardwood flooring ushers you through the main level of this thoughtfully remodeled classic home. The living room, with its grandeur emphasized by farm-style wooden beams, showcases built-in cabinets adorned with a timeless stone façade, creating an inviting focal point. The chef's kitchen is a culinary haven, featuring classic granite countertops, custom cabinetry, and a chic island topped with a butcher block. This kitchen offers a stunning view of the expansive backyard and its charming garden space. Luxury vinyl plank flooring unifies the living spaces, extending to both the upper and lower levels. The downstairs area provides a versatile living space, complete with its office space and abundant storage options. The side yard offers a fantastic spot for parking an RV or storing your cherished outdoor toys, rounding out this remarkable property.
